 Email read help
 ---------------

 Auto-reply - lets you automatically write a reply to the sender of the
letter you just received.

 Help - this stuff.

 Kill - deletes the current letter you are reading.

 Next - advances to the next letter in your mailbox, if there is one.

 Previous - backs up to the previous letters in your mailbox, if there
is one.

 Quit - ends reading your mail and returns to the Main menu.

 Reread - rereads the current letter.
